data.description: Spacious 4 bed, 3 bath ranch style family home.  Updated Kitchen, bathrooms, doors and trim. Shiplap accents in Living Room, Hall Bath and Primary Bedroom.  New carpet in the basement.  The upstairs living area includes a Primary bedroom with attached 3/4 bath plus 2 additional bedrooms and full bath with dual sinks.  Living room opens to Kitchen with stylish countertops, backsplash, newer cabinets and appliances.   The basement has a large rec room,  laundry/mech room and 1 additional bedroom that shares a closet with the newly remodeled 3/4 bath.  Newer main Floor windows, newer roof and A/C all added in the past few years.  The 1 car garage is deep with heat and A/C vent!  A Large fenced backyard is a bonus for the kids and pets to enjoy!  A large metal shed is included to store all your yard equipment.  No HOA.  This home is conveniently located within minutes of military bases, shopping, restaurants and schools. Schedule your showing today!
